{"tid":696652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"專家糾正　原來女孩做多了下體不會鬆","createTime":"2018-06-10T09:53:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-10T11:15:56.000Z","uid":53003,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"afba2b5e8ef80235dc6d1dd39b67372279bab030","tid":696652,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T09:53:29.000Z","msg":"一般人都認為，性行為次數過多，會影響女性陰道鬆緊度，不過性治療師指出，這個概念是錯的。<br />\n據《新假期週刊》報導，性治療師方陽醫生指出，陰道肌肉其實和身體肌肉一樣，用得越多練得越多，都會越來越緊緻，所以性行為不會影響陰道鬆弛，反而是隨著年紀或是產後，問題才會出現。至於怎樣知道是鬆還是緊，醫生表示只要是會漏尿、高潮次數減少、男方覺得感覺不同，可能就代表妳鬆。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180610/1370425/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180610%2F1370425%2F&d=GHMWbN1cdsnn79muNd4gfzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=009d676c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180610%2F1370425%2F&h=c55d4adb\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180610/1370425/</a>"},{"pid":"97da2df1d8f491289f8be85f2d29a232cff72e4e","tid":696652,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T09:56:43.000Z","msg":"愈用愈緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a879a1874b6d9018f17ef48826b8131ce30d4c","tid":696652,"uid":113626,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T09:56:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇過日本av表示唔係好信"},{"pid":"fe860080c8886c451a2b55e64e9c399c817f6bac","tid":696652,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T10:05:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 世界觀受到顛覆"},{"pid":"6200992df3ac2534189af2080dc648b8ef74b148","tid":696652,"uid":34927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T10:10:05.000Z","msg":"但唔係得陰道前段有可控制既肌肉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />